OL,4,CTrendy shoffices and pizza ovens raised
OL,5,Clockdown fire risks
OL,6, Trendy neighbours may have bought fire
OL,7, pits and pizza ovens during lockdown,
OL,8, or worked from home in a shoffice - but
OL,9, the risk of an expensive blaze grew.
OL,11,FInsurer Zurich has warned that
OL,12,Foutbuilding fires - in sheds, garages
OL,13,Fand conservatories - rose by 16% last
OL,14,Fyear compared with 2019.
OL,16,FIt said the popularity of conversions
OL,17,Fto home offices, gyms and domestic
OL,18,Fdrinks bars increased the fire risk.
OL,20,FThree-quarters of areas in the UK
OL,21,Frecorded more fires, the data shows.
